                            <comment id="14599431" author="tn" created="Wed, 24 Jun 2015 13:43:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in the following commits:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;4.0: 471e6b078a7891aea99b77f200e828&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;3.6: 229232829c6d8741138decf27c4909&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Now the Gamma.digamma and trigamma methods will propagate the input argument if it is not a real value.&lt;/p&gt;

